Program Vision: A Regional Hub for Forensic Nursing and Survivor-Centered Care

Purpose Statement:
Louisiana Delta Community College will become a regional leader in forensic nursing education and survivor-centered care by integrating a Sexual Assault Nurse Examiner (SANE) training program and clinical examination site into its state-of-the-art, currently vacant Forensic Science Laboratory.

